Dialogue 11: Submitting an Academic Paper（学术论文提交场景）「学术类词汇/词组全覆盖」
Male (Professor’s Assistant): Good morning, Academic Office. Can I help you with paper submission or thesis consultation? We have a strict deadline for this semester’s research papers.
