Male (Bank Clerk): Good afternoon, City Bank. Can I help you open a bank account, deposit money, withdraw cash, or apply for a credit card? We have current accounts, savings accounts and student accounts available.
Female (Customer): Good afternoon. I want to open a current account—I just moved to this city for work, and I need an account to receive my salary and pay my bills. What documents do I need to provide, and what are the benefits of a current account?
